-- Euronext adds Valeo to CAC 40, removes Vallourec
-- By Maya Nikolaeva
-- Thu Jun 05, 2014 02:11PM EDT
-- None



PARIS, June 5 (Reuters) - French auto parts maker Valeo <VLOF.PA> will be added to the CAC 40 index <.FCHI> while pipe and tube maker Vallourec <VLLP.PA> will be removed, the Expert Indices Committee of Euronext, a subsidiary of Intercontinental Exchange, said on Thursday.

